USD --> INR

1M - 10L
10M - 100L --> 1CR
50M - 500L ---> 5CR
100M - 1000L --> 10CR


500M - 50CR
1000M ----> 1B - 100CR



Formula's:

- Lakhs Conversion
    - 10M*10 -> X Lakhs
        Examples:
            - 10M * 10 = 100 Lakhs(1 Crore) 
            
- Crore Conversion
    - 10M/10 -> X Crores
        Examples:
            - 10M/10 -> 1 Crore
